name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Rasheed HARRIS, Petitioner

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 6th day of February, 2012, the Petition for Leave to File Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc is GRANTED. Petitioner is directed to file his Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 30 days of this order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
